<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 09:54:51 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>头顶的云</title><link>https://some.pics/6a3e4c68db3be</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我头顶上的云&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Clouds above my head " height="920" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/piotr/6a3e4c68db3be.jpg" width="700"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://piotr.some.pics"&gt;@piotr&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 09:54:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3e23611bf05</link><description>&lt;p&gt;粉色与橙色的日落氛围&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Sun setting behind the horizon causing a small area of intense orange and pink. A large amount of sky with a gradient from yellowy blue to dark blue. The landscape is silhouetted " height="3912" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/tristy/6a3e23611bf05.jpg" width="2929"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://tristy.some.pics"&gt;@tristy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 06:59:49 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3e19b30ea2a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一尊真人大小的"灵魂乐之王"奥蒂斯·雷丁铜像矗立在梅肯市中心的奥蒂斯·雷丁艺术中心。这尊由布拉德利·库利与小布拉德利·库利共同雕刻的塑像，捕捉了这位传奇歌手静坐怀抱吉他的平和姿态，致敬他与成长之城之间持久的情缘。该雕像最初于2002年揭幕，后迁至艺术中心的新址。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A bronze statue of a man playing guitar, set in front of the blue Otis Redding Center for the Arts sign. Bright, sunny day with greenery around." height="3648" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a3e19b30ea2a.jpg" width="5472"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 06:18:30 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3dd5609c35a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;#FensterFreitag&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="An old, small, white wooden double window, in whose glass a very orange and partly pink sunrise is reflected. The trees appear as black silhouettes against the light. The picture was taken at 3 am" height="2127" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a3dd5609c35a.jpg" width="3104"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 01:27:00 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3dd297bf951</link><description>&lt;p&gt;它有眼睛！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A bowl of ramen with a halved soft-boiled egg." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a3dd297bf951.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 01:15:07 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>